  ('dietitian-moex-00433', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關嬰兒添加副食品之原則，下列敘述何者最正確？', '["製作副食品時，以添加少鹽、少糖為原則", "儘量給與各種類食品，以提高對各種食品的接受性", "給與大量果汁及果乾，以提高維生素C之攝取", "攝食各類魚產品時，以攝取大型魚類為主"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a4584eaadc9d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8cbef348e467", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
