  ('dietitian-moex-00436', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '不同類型之運動選手，體內肌肉的型態可能會有些不同，下列何者含有較高比率的type I（slow-twitch） 肌肉？', '["馬拉松選手", "100公尺短跑選手", "跳高選手", "舉重選手"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "a4584eaadc9d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8cbef348e467", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "44", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "營養學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00437', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於含鐵食物的消化吸收，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["紅肉的血基質（heme）可直接被吸收入小腸上皮細胞", "2+ 3+ 植物類食物中的Fe 較Fe 難吸收", "小腸上皮細胞吸收的鐵會經由運鐵蛋白（transferrin）運送至骨髓造血", "小腸上皮細胞內的鐵與鐵蛋白（ferritin）結合後，會隨細胞脫落到糞便中"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4b45a176e23e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "84b9ea3552b5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00438', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '倒立時仍然可以吞嚥食物，是因為下列何種動作避免食物進入鼻腔？', '["唾液隨重力往下流", "軟顎上提與蠕動波", "聲門與括約肌放鬆", "會厭與支氣管收縮"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4b45a176e23e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "84b9ea3552b5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-00439', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '正常情況下，當腎絲球濾過液離開近曲腎小管之後，下列何種物質在腎小管管腔中的濃度會增加？', '["葡萄糖", "鈉離子", "重碳酸根離子（bicarbonate）", "肌酸酐（creatinine）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:50+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "4b45a176e23e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "84b9ea3552b5", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113030", "c": "102", "s": "33", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
